cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MA, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new human-swarm interaction framework using Virtual Reality and Leap Motion. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper involves coordinating and controlling mobile robots in a remote environment. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper uses Virtual Reality to create a virtual environment for the user to interact with the swarm robots. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is another possible category as the paper deals with coordinating and controlling a swarm of mobile robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper involves controlling a system of mobile robots.
